data.description: Like new but better! Charming 4 bedroom, 2 bath split bedroom design. 1909 sq. ft. of inviting living space.  Impeccably clean and lovingly maintained, both inside and out! Beautiful wood flooring throughout. Kitchen features solid wood cabinetry, w/mulitple slide outs, granite countertops, extensive island and ss appliances, pantry.  Retreat in the 18x15 Primary bedroom with attached bathroom that features walk-in shower and oversized bathtub. Plenty of room in the walk-in closet.  Tiled floor in laundry room with upper cabinets.  4th bedroom can easily be used as a dining room or office. Home has custom book case built-ins & custom closet shelving. Enjoy outdoor living on the covered patio w/ stamped concrete, beautifully landscaped East facing, fenced backyard. Three car garage w/Lift Master garage door openers. New TRANE Furnace and AC and thermostat in 2021. This home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style.
